lead_paragraph: A century stand from Steve Smith and Usman Khawaja propelled Australia to a nine-wicket victory over Ireland in their one-off One-Day International played at Willowmoore Park on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Smith and Khawaja Ease Australia to Win Over Ireland
